(8, 1, '2023-05-10 09:30:49', '2023-05-10 09:30:49', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.13.1 - 09-05-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h4>ABOUT US </h4>		\n		<p><strong>Welcome to SPHERE NEWS, your go-to source for the latest news and stories from around the world. We are a team of dedicated journalists and writers committed to delivering accurate, reliable, and timely news content to our readers.</strong></p><p><strong>Our mission is to keep you informed and connected to the world around you, covering local, national, and international news stories from a wide range of topics, including politics, sports, health and wellness.</strong></p><p><strong>At SPHERE NEWS, we value integrity, accuracy, and transparency in our reporting. We strive to provide a balanced perspective on news stories, free from bias and misinformation, and we uphold the highest standards of journalistic ethics.</strong></p><p><strong>Thank you for visiting us and we hope you enjoy our content and find it valuable in your daily life.</strong></p>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.13.1 - 09-05-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads